3.1.0

Changelog:
- 3.1.0: Added 4 expert rules for non-neuronal cell types (Astrocyte, Pericyte,
  Vascular_Endothelial, Fibroblast) in peng2020.py; extended _SPECIES_SYNONYMS in
  marker_scoring.py with missing common-name aliases (peromyscus, rhabdomys,
  cynomolgus, mus_musculus); unified Latin binomial names with ortholog.py
  (opossum→Monodelphis domestica, tree_shrew→Tupaia chinensis); added species
  validation warning in resolve_config() (core/utils.py); expanded retina config
  template marker_dict with 7 non-neuronal types (Microglia, Astrocytes, Pericytes,
  RPE, Endothelial, Oligodendrocytes, Fibroblast).
- 3.0.0: Added taxonomic classification (class/order) to all source_meta entries;
  merge engine now propagates class/order per cell type with _meta top-level KV;
  marker_scoring.py gains phylogenetic_weight() for taxonomic distance weighting;
  Config gains target_class + target_order for user-controlled phylogenetic filtering;
  added 3 new source files (zuo2024, hahn2023, menon2019) — 22 total cell types
  across Mammalia, Reptilia, Teleostei, Cyclostomata;
  synonyms expanded with developmental (PRPC/NRPC) and cross-species (Lamprey_RGC) entries.
- 2.0.0: Initial merge engine. Merges 7 source files (peng2019, peng2020, hu2019,
  yan2020, chen2023, hoang2023, zhang2024) into unified KB with consensus scoring
  (gold/high/medium/low) and cross-source conflict detection.
- 1.0.0: (unreleased) Individual source files only, no merge engine.
